4. Clean project
mvn clean

STEP 5: JENKINS SETUP
✅ Create Pipeline Job
Open Jenkins
Click New Item
Name: simple-maven-app
Select Pipeline
pipeline {
    agent any

    stages {

        stage('Clone Code') {
            steps {
                git 'https://github.com/yourusername/simple-maven-app.git'
            }
        }

        stage('Build with Maven') {
            steps {
                sh 'mvn clean install'
            }
        }
    }
}
Run Jenkins
Click Save
Click Build Now
✅ Output

✔ Code cloned
✔ Build success
✔ Test executed

